ZH: 和平共处是我们共同的责任。
EN: Coexisting peacefully is our shared responsibility.

ZH: 我们应该努力实现和平共处。
EN: We should strive to achieve peaceful coexistence.

ZH: 邻里之间要和平共处。
EN: Neighbors should coexist peacefully with each other.

ZH: 我们都应该学会和平共处。
EN: We all should learn to coexist peacefully.

ZH: 和平共处是国际社会的宗旨之一。
EN: Peaceful coexistence is one of the goals of the international community.

ZH: 我们必须遵循和平共处的原则。
EN: We must follow the principle of peaceful coexistence.

ZH: 和平共处是人类社会的基础。
EN: Peaceful coexistence is the foundation of human society.

ZH: 唯有和平共处，才能实现共赢。
EN: Only through peaceful coexistence can we achieve mutual benefits.

ZH: 我们要向世界传递和平共处的理念。
EN: We should spread the concept of peaceful coexistence to the world.

ZH: 愿世界各国都能实现和平共处。
EN: May all countries in the world achieve peaceful coexistence.

ZH: 和平共处有助于缓解冲突。
EN: Peaceful coexistence helps to ease conflicts.

ZH: 我们要倡导和平共处的理念。
EN: We should promote the idea of peaceful coexistence.

ZH: 和平共处是解决分歧的有效途径。
EN: Peaceful coexistence is an effective way to resolve differences.

ZH: 社会稳定需要和平共处。
EN: Social stability requires peaceful coexistence.

ZH: 我们要通过对话实现和平共处。
EN: We should achieve peaceful coexistence through dialogue.

ZH: 和平共处是世界的希望。
EN: Peaceful coexistence is the hope of the world.

ZH: 只有和平共处，才能实现持久和谐。
EN: Only through peaceful coexistence can we achieve lasting harmony.

ZH: 和平共处要靠双方共同努力。
EN: Peaceful coexistence requires joint efforts from both sides.

ZH: 战争不是解决问题的方式，只有和平共处才是理智之选。
EN: War is not the way to solve problems, only peaceful coexistence is the rational choice.

ZH: 在多元文化共存的社会里，和平共处尤为重要。
EN: In a multicultural society, peaceful coexistence is particularly important.
